data.description:
This charming 3-bedroom, 2-bath home is located in the heart of Garland conveniently located near schools, shopping, and dining. This well-maintained property offers a spacious 1,360 square feet of living space, perfect for those seeking a comfortable and cozy place to call home. A warm and inviting living room, featuring ample natural light streaming through large windows and a smoking brick chimney. The adjacent dining area provides a cozy space for family meals or intimate gatherings. The kitchen is a great size ready to take on any meal with plenty of counter space and cabinet spaces. Down the hallway, you'll find 3 generously sized bedrooms, each offering ample closet space and a comfortable retreat for rest and relaxation.
Updates consist of: interior exterior AC units replaced about 2 yrs ago and roof replaced about 4-5 yrs ago.

1905 Castle Dr offers the perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and charm. This property is sure to captivate the hearts of discerning homebuyers.
